Schema markup: just create a snippet of it and call in in theme head tag.
-----------------
<script type="application/ld+json">
{%- if template == 'index' -%}
{
  "@context": "http://schema.org",
  "@type": "WebSite",
  "name": "{{ shop.name }}",
  "alternateName": "{{ shop.description }}",
  "url": "{{ shop.url }}"
}
{%- elsif template == 'product' %}
